title: “Dan’s imaginary SuperPAC.” (LIVE in Durham)
description: Shutdown negotiations falter as Trump takes his demagoguery to El Paso, Elizabeth Warren and Amy Klobuchar formally launch their presidential campaigns, and “The Best of Enemies” star Taraji P. Henson joins Jon, Jon, Tommy, and Dan live on stage in Durham, North Carolina.
author: hey@crooked.com (Crooked Media)
